{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That must have been like late 1940-- late 1943--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'40-- late 1944, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Late 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People, we-- we were marching all day, every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every day, we slept wherever we were happened to be close someplace where there was a farm so that the SS troopers could get something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we lost a lot of people on this march because the exposure to the cold weather and the-- and the food was not sufficient.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was no sanitary facilities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had, in one march I think I had those dutch shoes, those--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clogs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I don't remember exactly on which one, maybe this was the one or maybe the one-- because I was on two death marches which occurred later.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- many people, just fell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they-- they couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So first, they got weak, so then we went in the back of the ones that were stronger, younger, and we took those in the-- from the back and brought them back front, and give-- so other people could hold on to them, you know, two other people and walk with them.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- so they got tired, you know, and-- and everyone was afraid to get tired because there was a-- an officer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] If there was a lower ranking officer-- must have been like a Sturmbannfuhrer-- he was on a motorcycle in the back of the column, and he had a-- a mauser in a wooden holster with a quite a long pistol.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and he would just pull up his motorcycle, and take out his pistol and shoot right through the head in one bullet for everyone that fell out.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
